    所有已实现的接口:
    java.io.Serializable, org.apache.spark.internal.Logging, scala.Serializable
    public class EdgeRDD<ED>
extends org.apache.spark.rdd.RDD<Edge<ED>>
    An RDD that exposes the interfaces to others as storing a collection of edges. The data are actually stored as a collection of `EdgeParitition` instances.

        public scala.collection.Iterator<Edge<ED>> compute​(org.apache.spark.Partition part,
                                                   org.apache.spark.TaskContext context)
        Abstract method inherited from RDD class. Given a partition `part` of this `EdgeRDD` instance, return an iterator of edges contained in it. The function `rdd.iterator(part, context)` returns an iterator, we call `next()` to get the `EdgePartitition` instance because there is only a single `EdgePartition` instance in that iterator.
